CatalogDescription: Travel can be both very enjoyable and stressful. The elleven™ Stealth Checkpoint-Friendly Computer Backpack has set out to make you at ease while traveling, whether that travel is back and forth to work or abroad. Standard features such as a padded laptop compartment for computers up to 17" and dedicated iPad/tablet pocket are enhanced with features that give you peace of mind away from home. The main computer compartment utilizes a puncture proof zipper combined with innovative zipper pulls that can be locked to deter thieves from making a quick getaway. The hidden RFID protected passport pocket on the back panel lets you keep your passport and/or wallet out of sight and against your body at all times. A cleverly designed security strap integrated into the backpack strap lets you wrap your bag around yourself or a table leg. Plenty of flexible storage throughout keeps you organized. Trolley sleeve on back and adjustable sternum strap.

CatalogDescription: The elleven™ Prizm Checkpoint-Friendly Backpack is a true road warrior that is built to withstand the rigors of travel. ItemName: Griffin™ Survivor Case for iPad Mini
CatalogDescription: Ridiculously over-engineered? Or the perfect case for your iPad mini no matter where you're headed? We think it's a little bit of both. Simply put, the Griffin Survivor Case is the most protective case we've ever built. Tested and certified to meet or exceed US Department of Defense Standard 810F, Griffin's Survivor Military-Duty Case is designed from the inside out to protect your iPad mini from extreme conditions ... dirt, sand, rain, shock, vibration and a host of other environmental factors. Survivor is built on a shatter-resistant polycarbonate frame clad in rugged, shock absorbing silicone. A built-in screen protector seals your Multi-Touch display from the outside environment, while hinged plugs seal the dock connector, camera lens, headphone port, hold switch and volume controls. The included stand clips on, then folds open for landscape viewing and typing.
